To do widget has been upgraded: Recurring tasks Color tags Later section. Multiple improvements and bug fixes.

To do widget has been upgraded: Recurring tasks. Have tasks that repeat frequently Create a recurring task so you never forget about important todos and save time as LifeViewer will create your tasks for you! Swipe right on a created task or select repeats while creating a new todo. Color tags. Assign a color to your task to easily navigate through your list. Later section. Displays tasks created on days following the selected day so you can always see what s coming next. Have todos with no specific date Create a No date task by simply dragging the task into Later section. Hide tasks from Later section by swiping left and choosing Hide.

Password lock: Add an extra layer of protection by enabling a password lock in LifeViewer s Settings! App tips: Learn how to use LifeViewer efficiently! Tap on buttons scattered around the app to know more about its functionality. Life expectancy: Can be customised! Choose Settings Life expectancy Choose the number of years manually by tapping Custom or select your country and gender to get it from Statistics. Settings: Have been redesigned to make it easier for your to make needed changes.
Widget customisation has been upgraded: Choose position colour and size of your widgets Choose which widgets will appear on your Day screen Simply go to LifeViewer s Settings menu and tap on Widgets
Habits widget has been updated: Reorder your habit list. Tap on your habit s circle icon to complete a habit.

Habits widget has been updated: Swipe right on a habit to complete it swipe left to undo. Set reminders for habits. Long tap on a notification to complete a habit or remind later Schedule widget has been updated: Widget has been completely redesigned
Widget customisation. Personalise LifeViewer to suit your productivity needs: Go to Settings Widgets to choose widgets that will appear on your Day screen

Add an emoji that symbolises your day make it special Week screen has been updated to provide you with an overview of your week s results and activities Onboarding has been completely redesigned Multiple bug fixes and performance improvements
